headline: MAA Announces Regular Quarterly Preferred Dividend
summary: Mid-America Apartment Communities, Inc., or MAA (NYSE: MAA), today announced a full quarterly dividend of $1.0625 per outstanding share of its 8.50% Series I Cumulative Redeemable Preferred Stock. The dividend is payable on September 30, 2025, to shareholders of record on September 15, 2025.
